"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-27-Chinese-delegation-seen-in-red-at-Olympics-opening-ceremony-1vzKf7nQstq-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  CGTN  Copied  Members of the Chinese delegation are seen at the opening ceremony of the Paris 2024 Olympic Games on July 26. /IC  At the 2024 Paris Olympics opening ceremony, the Chinese delegation members were spotted wearing red jackets on boats moving along the River Seine. China has sent a 716-member delegation with 405 athletes, including 42 Olympic champions.  Members of the Chinese delegation are seen at the opening ceremony of the Paris 2024 Olympic Games on July 26. /IC  The red color not only echoes with the national flag of China, it is also considered a lucky and auspicious color in Chinese culture, representing joy, celebration, vitality, and success.  Members of the Chinese delegation are seen at the opening ceremony of the Paris 2024 Olympic Games on July 26. /IC  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"